---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Redactorizer — Safely redact documents and images on your Mac"
  description="Redact documents and images locally on your Mac. Built for investigative journalists and whistleblowers. No data leaves your computer. PDF and image support."
  current="home"
>
  <article>
    <!-- Hero -->
    <section class="relative overflow-hidden border-b border-border">
      <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-linear-to-b from-accent-muted/30 via-transparent to-transparent" aria-hidden="true" />
      <div class="relative mx-auto max-w-5xl px-4 py-20 sm:px-6 sm:py-28">
        <div class="space-y-12">
          <div>
            <h1 class="font-display text-4xl font-normal tracking-tight text-fg sm:text-5xl lg:text-6xl">
              Redact safely.<br />
              <span class="italic text-accent">Nothing leaves your Mac.</span>
            </h1>
            <p class="mt-6 max-w-2xl text-lg leading-relaxed text-fg-muted">
              Redactorizer lets you redact documents and images locally—no uploads, no cloud, no trace.
              Built for investigative journalists and anyone who needs to protect sources and sensitive information.
            </p>
            <div class="mt-10 flex flex-wrap gap-4">
          <a
            href="https://apps.apple.com/nl/app/redactorizer/id6758915996"
            target="_blank"
            rel="noopener noreferrer"
            class="inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-xl bg-accent px-6 py-3.5 text-sm font-semibold text-white shadow-lg shadow-accent/25 transition hover:bg-accent-hover focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-accent focus:ring-offset-2 focus:ring-offset-surface"
          >
            Get on Mac App Store — $5
          </a>
          <a
            href="https://github.com/j-norwood-young/redactorizer"
            target="_blank"
            rel="noopener noreferrer"
            class="inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-xl border border-border-strong bg-surface-elevated px-6 py-3.5 text-sm font-semibold text-fg transition hover:border-border hover:bg-surface-muted focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-fg-subtle focus:ring-offset-2 focus:ring-offset-surface"
          >
            Source on GitHub — Free
          </a>
          <a
            href="/contact/"
            class="inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-xl border border-accent/40 bg-accent-muted px-6 py-3.5 text-sm font-semibold text-accent transition hover:bg-accent/10 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-accent focus:ring-offset-2 focus:ring-offset-surface"
          >
            Journalists - Free
          </a>
            </div>
            <p class="mt-4 text-sm text-fg-subtle">
              Paying supports future development. You can also build from source and run it for free.
              <strong class="text-fg-muted">Investigative journalists:</strong> contact me and I’ll send you a free copy.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="relative -mx-4 sm:mx-0">
            <div
              class="pointer-events-none absolute inset-0 rounded-[2rem] border border-border/70 bg-linear-to-b from-accent-muted/15 via-transparent to-background/80 shadow-[0_40px_120px_rgba(0,0,0,0.45)]"
              aria-hidden="true"
            />
            <img
              src="/redactorizer-demo1.webp"
              alt="Redactorizer redaction workflow preview"
              class="relative z-[1] w-full rounded-[1.75rem] border border-border/60 bg-surface-elevated object-contain"
              loading="lazy"
            />
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Features -->
    <section class="mx-auto max-w-4xl px-4 py-16 sm:px-6 sm:py-24">
      <h2 class="font-display text-3xl font-normal text-fg">Why Redactorizer?</h2>
      <ul class="mt-10 grid gap-6 sm:grid-cols-1">
        <li class="group flex gap-5 rounded-2xl border border-border bg-surface-elevated p-6 transition hover:border-border-strong hover:bg-surface-muted/50">
          <span class="flex h-12 w-12 shrink-0 items-center justify-center rounded-xl bg-accent-muted text-2xl" aria-hidden="true">🔒</span>
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-base font-semibold text-fg">100% local</h3>
            <p class="mt-1 text-sm leading-relaxed text-fg-muted">
              All redaction happens on your Mac. No data is sent to any server—ever.
            </p>
          </div>
        </li>
        <li class="group flex gap-5 rounded-2xl border border-border bg-surface-elevated p-6 transition hover:border-border-strong hover:bg-surface-muted/50">
          <span class="flex h-12 w-12 shrink-0 items-center justify-center rounded-xl bg-accent-muted text-2xl" aria-hidden="true">📄</span>
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-base font-semibold text-fg">PDFs and images</h3>
            <p class="mt-1 text-sm leading-relaxed text-fg-muted">
              Redact text and areas in PDFs and common image formats.
            </p>
          </div>
        </li>
        <li class="group flex gap-5 rounded-2xl border border-border bg-surface-elevated p-6 transition hover:border-border-strong hover:bg-surface-muted/50">
          <span class="flex h-12 w-12 shrink-0 items-center justify-center rounded-xl bg-accent-muted text-2xl" aria-hidden="true">🛡️</span>
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-base font-semibold text-fg">Protect sources</h3>
            <p class="mt-1 text-sm leading-relaxed text-fg-muted">
              Designed for investigative journalists and whistleblowers who need to share documents without exposing identities or sensitive details.
            </p>
          </div>
        </li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <!-- CTA -->
    <section class="border-t border-border bg-surface-elevated">
      <div class="mx-auto max-w-4xl px-4 py-16 sm:px-6 sm:py-20">
        <h2 class="font-display text-3xl font-normal text-fg">Get started</h2>
        <p class="mt-3 max-w-xl text-fg-muted">
          Download from the Mac App Store for $5 to support development, clone the repo and build from source for free, or—if you’re a journalist—contact me for a free copy.
        </p>
        <div class="mt-6 rounded-2xl border border-accent/30 bg-accent-muted/50 p-4 sm:p-5">
          <p class="text-sm font-medium text-fg">For journalists</p>
          <p class="mt-1 text-sm text-fg-muted">
            If you’re an investigative journalist and would like Redactorizer at no cost, get in touch and I’ll send you a free copy—no questions asked.
          </p>
          <a
            href="/contact/"
            class="mt-3 inline-flex items-center text-sm font-semibold text-accent transition hover:text-accent-hover focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-accent focus:ring-offset-2 focus:ring-offset-surface-elevated rounded"
          >
            Contact me to request →
          </a>
        </div>
        <div class="mt-8 flex flex-wrap gap-4">
          <a
            href="Redactorizer"
            target="_blank"
            rel="noopener noreferrer"
            class="inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-xl bg-accent px-6 py-3.5 text-sm font-semibold text-white transition hover:bg-accent-hover focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-accent focus:ring-offset-2 focus:ring-offset-surface"
          >
            Mac App Store — $5
          </a>
          <a
            href="https://github.com/j-norwood-young/redactorizer"
            target="_blank"
            rel="noopener noreferrer"
            class="inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-xl border border-border-strong bg-surface px-6 py-3.5 text-sm font-semibold text-fg transition hover:bg-surface-muted focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-fg-subtle focus:ring-offset-2 focus:ring-offset-surface"
          >
            GitHub — Free
          </a>
          <a
            href="/contact/"
            class="inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-xl border border-border-strong bg-surface px-6 py-3.5 text-sm font-semibold text-fg transition hover:bg-surface-muted focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-fg-subtle focus:ring-offset-2 focus:ring-offset-surface"
          >
            Journalists: request free
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </article>
</Layout>
